<br>
A lvl 8 necromancer pet and a lvl 8 magician pet... two of my young friends needed some help in obtaining some newbie items... I summoned them (the pets) both a phantom plate armour set and an elemental shield, then I both gave them a 2hb summoned staff of symbols (which is a Lore item).  <br>
They still wore the shield on their arm, and the 2hb in the other, and both were hitting for 20 dmg!!! on the odd occasion (lvl 8 pets!!).<br>
<br>
So, I guess higher-damage weapons are better for yer pet to play around with, seeing as they seem to do more damage...<br>
<br>
What I will be trying is give my pet 2 staffs from now on (I can summon another 1HB'er which is slightly less good, but still... and pet can dual wield...) just to see if it has more damage output as well - and then I'll come back and let ya know.<br>
<br>
